OL,3,GUK weather for today and tomorrow
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FEarly fog in the far southwest
OL,6,Fclears quickly. Most areas stay dry
OL,7,Fwith sunshine and variable cloud,
OL,8,Fthough northern and northeastern
OL,9,Fregions may see isolated showers.
OL,10,FLight winds overall, breezier
OL,11,Fnortheast. Warm in the southwest,
OL,12,Fcooler northern and eastern coasts.
OL,13,
OL,14,CTonight:FMostly dry with light winds,
OL,15,Fgusty in the far southwest spreading
OL,16,Fnortheast. Cloudier northern and
OL,17,Feastern coasts with some rain
OL,18,Fpossible; otherwise clear spells.
OL,19,FChance of showers southwest by dawn.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
