OL,3,GUK weather for today and tomorrow
OL,4,
OL,5,CMonday:FStaying dry with sunny spells.
OL,6,FShowers track east across southern
OL,7,Fareas, possibly thundery. Cloud
OL,8,Fthickens in the west and north with
OL,9,Fevening rain. Winds light to moderate,
OL,10,Ftemperatures near average.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
